                    <comment id="13211573" author="martijn.v.groningen" created="Sun, 19 Feb 2012 22:19:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch adds a collector that computes grouped facet counts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Work to be done:&lt;/p&gt;
