&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                    <comment id="13221986" author="martijn.v.groningen" created="Sun, 4 Mar 2012 19:44:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated patch. This patch includes a random test for grouped faceting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="13222061" author="martijn.v.groningen" created="Sun, 4 Mar 2012 23:43:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated patch.&lt;/p&gt;
